summary: A Racemenu preset of a pretty Wood Elf.
descriptionHtml:
First I'd like to start apologizing about my english, it's not my native language and I'm self taught.

This is a Wood Elf preset for racemenu.
 
The mods I used:

Body: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition[/url]
Body Texture: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/55761/?]Real Girls Realistic Body Texture[/url]
Hair: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url]
Eyebrows: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url]
Eyes: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url]
Warpaints: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34539/?]Battle Hardened Warpaints[/url]
Freckles: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url]

The armors in the screenshots:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/44567/?]Gilded Doublet[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71843/?]The Lily - Armour Mashup[/url]

The ENB:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41470/?]Poupouri ENBs - Extended[/url]

INSTALLATION: You can use NMM to install this preset or you can just drop the files on your data folder. 

[b]ALL CREDITS go to the creators of the mods listed above. Without them this character wouldn't be possible.
Don't forget to ENDORSE their marvelous work. ;)[/b]
author: BlindValkyrie
